## ROLLBACK CAPABILITY

This tag can be used for emergency rollback:

```bash
# View tag
git tag -l | grep comp-plan

# Reset to snapshot (DESTRUCTIVE - will lose all changes after tag)
git reset --hard comp-plan-v1-snapshot

# Or checkout as new branch
git checkout -b rollback-branch comp-plan-v1-snapshot
```

